==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Multigraph
<hw>Mul"ti*graph</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Multi-</ets> + <ets>-graph</ets>.]</ety> <def>A combined
rotary type-setting and printing machine for office use. The type is
transferred semi-automatically by means of keys from a type-supply drum
to a printing drum. The printing may be done by means of an inked ribbon
to print ⟦ldquo⟧typewritten⟦rdquo⟧ letters, or directly from inked type
or a stereotype plate, as in a printing press.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Multijugate</ent>⟦br⟧
